#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Pāsādakampanavagga"
msgstr "2. Shaking the Stilt Longhouse"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 16. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta → mahiddhikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn51.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "16. Ascetics and Brahmins (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.16:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā ahesuṃ mahānubhāvā, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the ascetics and brahmins in the past,"

msgctxt "sn51.16:1.2"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā bhavissanti mahānubhāvā, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn51.16:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā mahānubhāvā, sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "or present who are mighty and powerful have become so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.274"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.16:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.6"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā ahesuṃ mahānubhāvā, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "All the ascetics and brahmins in the past,"

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.7"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā bhavissanti mahānubhāvā, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn51.16:2.8"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā mahiddhikā mahānubhāvā, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā”ti."
msgstr "or present who are mighty and powerful have become so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.16:2.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
